<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
  <title>SimplCyber Technical Security Report – {{domain}}</title>

  <!-- Typography: JetBrains Mono for code, Inter for text -->
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #f6f7f9;
      --card: #ffffff;
      --ink: #0f172a;
      --ink-2: #334155;
      --ink-3: #64748b;
      --accent: #0f766e;
      --accent-2: #115e59;
      --accent-soft: #e6fffb;
      --border: #e5e7eb;
      --critical: #b91c1c;
      --high: #c2410c;
      --medium: #a16207;
      --low: #15803d;
      --info: #0369a1;
      --code-bg: #f8fafc;
      --code-border: #e2e8f0;
      --radius-lg: 14px;
      --radius-md: 10px;
      --shadow-1: 0 2px 10px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.05);
      --fs-0: 0.875rem;
      --fs-1: 1rem;
      --fs-2: 1.125rem;
      --fs-3: 1.375rem;
      --fs-4: 1.75rem;
      --fs-5: clamp(1.5rem, 3.2vw, 2.25rem);
      --fs-6: clamp(1.75rem, 4.0vw, 3rem);
      --space-1: 6px;
      --space-2: 10px;
      --space-3: 14px;
      --space-4: 20px;
      --space-5: 28px;
      --space-6: 36px;
      --space-7: 48px;
      --space-8: 64px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html, body { height: 100%; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
    }

    .report {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: var(--space-7) auto;
      padding: 0 var(--space-4);
    }

    .header {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-1);
      padding: var(--space-6) var(--space-6);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    }
    .header-top {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--space-3);
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    }
    .brand {
      display: flex;
      gap: var(--space-3);
      align-items: center;
    }
    .brand-mark {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: radial-gradient(120% 120% at 20% 20%, #14b8a6 0%, #0f766e 60%, #115e59 100%);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
    }
    .title {
      display: grid;
      gap: 2px;
    }
    .title h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: var(--fs-5);
      letter-spacing: -0.015em;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .subtitle {
      color: var(--ink-3);
      font-size: var(--fs-0);
    }
    .report-meta {
      text-align: right;
      color: var(--ink-3);
      font-size: var(--fs-0);
    }
    .meta-pill {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--code-bg);
      color: var(--ink-2);
      font-weight: 600;
      border: 1px solid var(--code-border);
      margin-left: var(--space-2);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    }

    .scan-overview {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-1);
      padding: var(--space-6);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    }

    .scan-overview h2 {
      font-size: var(--fs-3);
      margin: 0 0 var(--space-4) 0;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .scan-stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
      gap: var(--space-4);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    }

    .stat-card {
      background: var(--code-bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--code-border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      padding: var(--space-3);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .stat-value {
      font-size: var(--fs-3);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
    }

    .stat-label {
      font-size: var(--fs-0);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      color: var(--ink-3);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .stat-card.critical .stat-value { color: var(--critical); }
    .stat-card.high .stat-value { color: var(--high); }
    .stat-card.medium .stat-value { color: var(--medium); }
    .stat-card.low .stat-value { color: var(--low); }

    .module-summary {
      background: var(--code-bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--code-border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      padding: var(--space-4);
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: var(--fs-0);
    }

    .findings-section {
      margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    }

    .findings-section h2 {
      font-size: var(--fs-4);
      margin: 0 0 var(--space-4) 0;
      color: var(--ink);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--space-2);
    }

    .section-count {
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      color: var(--accent-2);
      padding: 4px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: var(--fs-0);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .finding {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-1);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .finding-header {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
      gap: var(--space-3);
      align-items: center;
      padding: var(--space-4);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--code-bg);
    }

    .severity-badge {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    }

    .severity-badge.critical { background: #fef2f2; color: var(--critical); border: 1px solid #fecaca; }
    .severity-badge.high { background: #fff7ed; color: var(--high); border: 1px solid #fed7aa; }
    .severity-badge.medium { background: #fffbeb; color: var(--medium); border: 1px solid #fde68a; }
    .severity-badge.low { background: #f0fdf4; color: var(--low); border: 1px solid #bbf7d0; }
    .severity-badge.info { background: #f0f9ff; color: var(--info); border: 1px solid #bae6fd; }

    .finding-title {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: var(--fs-2);
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .finding-type {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: var(--fs-0);
      color: var(--ink-3);
      background: white;
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .finding-body {
      padding: var(--space-5);
    }

    .finding-description {
      color: var(--ink-2);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .technical-details {
      background: var(--code-bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--code-border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      padding: var(--space-4);
      margin: var(--space-4) 0;
    }

    .technical-details h4 {
      margin: 0 0 var(--space-3) 0;
      font-size: var(--fs-1);
      color: var(--ink);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--space-2);
    }

    .tech-icon {
      font-size: 1.2em;
    }

    .code-block {
      background: #1a202c;
      color: #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      padding: var(--space-4);
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: var(--fs-0);
      overflow-x: auto;
      margin: var(--space-3) 0;
      border: 1px solid #2d3748;
    }

    .code-block .comment { color: #68d391; }
    .code-block .keyword { color: #90cdf4; }
    .code-block .string { color: #f6e05e; }

    .url-list {
      background: var(--code-bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--code-border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      padding: var(--space-3);
      margin: var(--space-3) 0;
    }

    .url-list ul {
      margin: 0;
      padding-left: var(--space-4);
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: var(--fs-0);
    }

    .url-list li {
      margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
      color: var(--ink-2);
    }

    .remediation {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-soft) 0%, #f0fdf9 100%);
      border: 1px solid #a7f3d0;
      border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      padding: var(--space-5);
      margin-top: var(--space-4);
    }

    .remediation h4 {
      margin: 0 0 var(--space-3) 0;
      font-size: var(--fs-2);
      color: var(--accent-2);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--space-2);
    }

    .remediation-steps {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .remediation-steps li {
      position: relative;
      padding-left: var(--space-5);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
      color: var(--ink-2);
    }

    .remediation-steps li::before {
      content: counter(step-counter);
      counter-increment: step-counter;
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 0;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: white;
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .remediation-steps {
      counter-reset: step-counter;
    }

    .priority-indicator {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: var(--space-1);
      font-size: var(--fs-0);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    }

    .priority-dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .priority-immediate .priority-dot { background: var(--critical); }
    .priority-critical .priority-dot { background: var(--critical); }
    .priority-high .priority-dot { background: var(--high); }
    .priority-medium .priority-dot { background: var(--medium); }
    .priority-low .priority-dot { background: var(--low); }

    .remediation-description {
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      border: 1px solid #a7f3d0;
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      padding: var(--space-3);
      margin: var(--space-3) 0;
      color: var(--ink-2);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .risk-assessment {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      padding: var(--space-4);
      margin: var(--space-4) 0;
    }

    .risk-metrics {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: var(--space-3);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    }

    .risk-metric {
      text-align: center;
      padding: var(--space-2);
      background: var(--code-bg);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    }

    .risk-value {
      font-size: var(--fs-2);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--accent-2);
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    }

    .risk-label {
      font-size: var(--fs-0);
      color: var(--ink-3);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .cvss-score {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-size: var(--fs-0);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-left: var(--space-2);
    }

    .cvss-critical { background: #fef2f2; color: var(--critical); }
    .cvss-high { background: #fff7ed; color: var(--high); }
    .cvss-medium { background: #fffbeb; color: var(--medium); }
    .cvss-low { background: #f0fdf4; color: var(--low); }

    .tools-used {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-1);
      padding: var(--space-6);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
    }

    .tools-used h3 {
      font-size: var(--fs-3);
      margin: 0 0 var(--space-4) 0;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .tool-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
      gap: var(--space-3);
    }

    .tool-card {
      background: var(--code-bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--code-border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      padding: var(--space-3);
    }

    .tool-name {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--ink);
      margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
    }

    .tool-description {
      font-size: var(--fs-0);
      color: var(--ink-3);
    }

    .footer {
      color: var(--ink-3);
      font-size: var(--fs-0);
      text-align: center;
      padding: var(--space-6) var(--space-4) var(--space-7);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      margin-top: var(--space-7);
    }

    @media print {
      body { background: #fff; font-size: 12px; }
      .report { margin: 0; padding: 0; }
      .header, .scan-overview, .finding, .tools-used { box-shadow: none; }
      .finding { page-break-inside: avoid; break-inside: avoid; }
      .code-block { background: #f8f9fa !important; color: #333 !important; border: 1px solid #ddd; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .scan-stats { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
      .risk-metrics { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .tool-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 560px) {
      .scan-stats { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .risk-metrics { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .finding-header { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--space-2); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="report">

    <section class="header">
      <div class="header-top">
        <div class="brand">
          <div class="brand-mark"></div>
          <div class="title">
            <h1>Technical Security Report</h1>
            <div class="subtitle">{{domain}}</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="report-meta">
          <span>Generated: {{report_date}}</span>
          <span class="meta-pill">v2.0 • {{modules_completed}} modules</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="scan-overview">
      <h2>Scan Overview</h2>
      
      <div class="scan-stats">
        <div class="stat-card critical">
          <div class="stat-value">{{severity_counts.CRITICAL}}</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Critical</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card high">
          <div class="stat-value">{{severity_counts.HIGH}}</div>
          <div class="stat-label">High</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card medium">
          <div class="stat-value">{{severity_counts.MEDIUM}}</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Medium</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card low">
          <div class="stat-value">{{severity_counts.LOW}}</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Low</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-value">{{total_findings}}</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Total</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="module-summary">
Scan ID: {{scan_id}}
Target:  {{domain}}
Date:    {{scan_date}}
Runtime: {{duration_seconds}}s
Modules: {{modules_completed}} active security modules
Status:  Complete
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="tools-used">
      <h3>Security Tools & Methodology</h3>
      
      <div class="tool-grid">
        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-name">httpx</div>
          <div class="tool-description">HTTP toolkit for probing and discovery</div>
        </div>
        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-name">sslscan</div>
          <div class="tool-description">SSL/TLS configuration analysis</div>
        </div>
        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-name">nuclei</div>
          <div class="tool-description">Vulnerability scanner with template engine</div>
        </div>
        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-name">nmap</div>
          <div class="tool-description">Network discovery and port scanning</div>
        </div>
        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-name">whatweb</div>
          <div class="tool-description">Web application fingerprinting</div>
        </div>
        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-name">Custom Modules</div>
          <div class="tool-description">SimplCyber proprietary security checks</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {{#if findings.length}}
    <section class="findings-section">
      <h2>Security Findings <span class="section-count">{{total_findings}} issues</span></h2>

      {{#each findings}}
      <article class="finding">
        <header class="finding-header">
          <span class="severity-badge {{toLowerCase severity}}">{{severity}}</span>
          <div class="finding-title">{{title}}</div>
          <div class="finding-type">{{type}}</div>
        </header>
        
        <div class="finding-body">
          <div class="finding-description">
            {{#if description}}{{description}}{{else}}Security vulnerability identified requiring technical remediation.{{/if}}
          </div>

          <div class="technical-details">
            <h4><span class="tech-icon">🔍</span> Technical Analysis</h4>
            
            {{#if metadata.url}}
            <div class="url-list">
              <strong>Affected URL:</strong>
              <ul>
                <li>{{metadata.url}}</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            {{#if metadata.endpoints}}
            <div class="url-list">
              <strong>Affected Endpoints:</strong>
              <ul>
                {{#each metadata.endpoints}}
                <li>{{this}}</li>
                {{/each}}
              </ul>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            {{#if metadata.technologies}}
            <div class="url-list">
              <strong>Affected Technologies:</strong>
              <ul>
                {{#each metadata.technologies}}
                <li>{{this}}</li>
                {{/each}}
              </ul>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            {{#if metadata.response}}
            <div>
              <strong>Server Response:</strong>
              <div class="code-block">{{metadata.response}}</div>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            {{#if metadata.headers}}
            <div>
              <strong>Security Headers:</strong>
              <div class="code-block">{{#each metadata.headers}}{{@key}}: {{this}}
{{/each}}</div>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
          </div>

          {{#if metadata.cvss_score}}
          <div class="risk-assessment">
            <h4><span class="tech-icon">📊</span> Risk Assessment</h4>
            <div class="risk-metrics">
              <div class="risk-metric">
                <div class="risk-value">{{metadata.cvss_score}}</div>
                <div class="risk-label">CVSS Score</div>
              </div>
              <div class="risk-metric">
                <div class="risk-value">{{metadata.exploitability}}%</div>
                <div class="risk-label">Exploitability</div>
              </div>
              <div class="risk-metric">
                <div class="risk-value">{{metadata.impact_score}}</div>
                <div class="risk-label">Impact</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          {{/if}}

          <div class="remediation">
            <h4>🛠️ AI-Generated Remediation Plan</h4>
            
            {{#if ai_remediation}}
            <div class="priority-indicator priority-{{toLowerCase ai_remediation.priority}}">
              <span class="priority-dot"></span>
              {{ai_remediation.priority}} PRIORITY - {{ai_remediation.timeline}}
            </div>

            {{#if ai_remediation.description}}
            <div class="remediation-description">
              {{ai_remediation.description}}
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            {{#if ai_remediation.steps}}
            <ol class="remediation-steps">
              {{#each ai_remediation.steps}}
              <li>{{this}}</li>
              {{/each}}
            </ol>
            {{/if}}

            {{#if ai_remediation.raw_response}}
            <details>
              <summary style="cursor: pointer; color: var(--accent-2); font-weight: 600; margin: var(--space-3) 0;">
                📝 View Full AI Analysis
              </summary>
              <div style="white-space: pre-wrap; background: var(--code-bg); padding: var(--space-3); border-radius: var(--radius-md); margin-top: var(--space-2); font-size: var(--fs-0); line-height: 1.5;">{{ai_remediation.raw_response}}</div>
            </details>
            {{/if}}

            {{else}}
            <!-- Fallback to generic remediation if AI fails -->
            <div class="priority-indicator priority-{{toLowerCase severity}}">
              <span class="priority-dot"></span>
              {{severity}} PRIORITY - Review and remediate as appropriate
            </div>

            <ol class="remediation-steps">
              <li>Analyze the specific vulnerability in your environment</li>
              <li>Implement appropriate security controls based on risk level</li>
              <li>Test fixes in staging environment before production</li>
              <li>Monitor for similar issues across your infrastructure</li>
              <li>Document remediation steps for future reference</li>
            </ol>
            {{/if}}
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      {{/each}}
    </section>
    {{else}}
    <section class="findings-section">
      <h2>Security Findings</h2>
      <div class="finding">
        <div class="finding-body">
          <div class="finding-description">
            ✅ No security vulnerabilities detected in this scan. Your security posture appears to be well-configured for the tested attack vectors.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    {{/if}}

    <footer class="footer">
